ProMED-mail
<promed@promedmail.org>

Guarda, Portugal is located north and fairly near the border with
Spain. See maps at
<http://www.fao.org/fi/fcp/en/PRT/PICS/portugal.jpg> and at the
source URL above. - Mod.PC]
